<title><anchor id="gtk-combo-box-popup-hide">gtk_combo_box_popup_hide ()</title>
<programlisting>void        gtk_combo_box_popup_hide        (<link linkend="GtkComboBox">GtkComboBox</link> *combo_box);</programlisting>
<para>
Hide popup, but not when it is torn off.
This is the external interface - for subclasses and apps which expect a
regular combo which doesn't do tearoffs.</para>
